reviews.review:
What on earth do I say about Dead by Daylight?
I could say about it's active (though partly salty) community;
Its vivid and genuinely enjoyable gameplay;
Its absolute replayability;
Its rich soundtrack;
Or its constant expansion, with new chapters and events.

However, rather than go into depth about this all, I have one thing to say. Buy this game. Go on, do it.
You won't regret it (Unless you play as a Dwight main from the get-go).
If you want a game that you can constantly go back to, a game that constantly changes based on feedback from the community and a downright fun game with replayability, this game is for you.

Oh, and if you do decide to buy this game... please make it your duty to understand the F I N G E R G U N S meme. You won't regret it.
